Yo桑下次唔黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0231df36af258e4edeb077a113579f2721233e2","tid":59120,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T16:08:10.000Z","msg":"My dear fans, <br />\n<br />\nLet me explain what happened with my concert tonight.<br />\n2 hours before the show, the promoter in Hong Kong told me, they realized that they failed to apply for a license for tonight's show.<br />\nAnd told me that I needed to cancel the show. <br />\nI was really confused for a moment. The promoter really apologized to me.<br />\nThen I proposed, what if I were to play a private show for free for my fans, who were already at the venue tonight,<br />\nCan the venue allow me to play?<br />\nAfter a long negotiation, the venue said they will allow me to play tomorrow night.<br />\nSo I will play a show in Hong Kong for the people who already have tickets for free. <br />\nAll tickets will be honored and refunded.<br />\nIn order for us to make up for any inconveniences, each ticket holder can bring one extra friend as a guest (Tickets will be refunded regardless).<br />\nWe'll try to accommodate anyway we can, even changing the stage plan.<br />\nAgain I'm really sorry for what has happened tonight.<br />\nI hope you understand and can make it tomorrow night.<br />\nThank you<br />\n<br />\nYOSHIKI<br />\n<br />\ninfo<br />\nYoshiki Classical ticket Hotline - 852 65375134<br />\nEmail: puffininfo@gmail.com"},{"pid":"e3d3da146b8379f1e5caaf2ad10a35d60f2d60d9","tid":59120,"uid":17167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T16:12:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 林生志不在錢"},{"pid":"745bb5e69dc87e1c936e4894de9abbaa3d511c29","tid":59120,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T16:14:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 